            "id": 6069564,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 尚凡(5278)股價殺至跌停，跌停價39.85元，成交5,256張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>尚凡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5278:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5278\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5278-TW</a>)18日11:52下跌4.4元，股價跌停報39.85元，委買241,000張、委賣6,000張，成交5,256張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為社群交友網路平台服務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>尚凡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5278:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5278\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5278-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲21.9%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.01%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+713 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+724 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-11 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6069564",
